title: Chất lượng không chưa mong đợi
content:
Chất lượng giấy như sách cũ. Mình đã mua hai lần bản tiếng anh, nhưng cả hai lần đều làm mình thất vọng.
Mong tiki có những cải tiến, thay đổi hoàn thiện những cuốn sách bản tiếng anh. Đem đến sự hài lòng cho người yêu sách như tôi. Để tiki là sự lựa chọn hàng đầu cho người mot sách mọi lúc, mọi nơi, mọi thời điểm.

title: Solid common sense advice.
content:
The book's main points are all common sense but it was helpful to see them all in one place. Great read for a college student or recent college grad just starting out in the workplace.
I can summarize the book's message as follows: be nice, help others, build your network, use your network
